title: Ghostly Swim
description:
Ghostly Swim features nineteen tracks from artists on Ghostly International, the avant-pop and non-dancefloor arm of Ann Arbor imprint Ghostly/Spectral. The 19-song collection features a variety of music, ranging from downtempo electronics from Ghostly regulars such as Matthew Dear, Dabrye, Osborne, Aeroc and Kill Memory Crash to friends of the label such as Detroit's Deastro, Milosh from Plug Research, Flying Lotus and SAMIYAM teaming up as FLYamSAM, and UK band The Chap.
